border-primary.description: Default border color, used to separate different elements, such as: form separator, card separator, etc

border-secondary.description: Slightly lighter than the default border color

radius-sm.description: SM size border radius, used in small size components, such as Button, Input, Select and other input components in small size.

radius-lg.description: LG size border radius, used in some large border radius components, such as Card, Modal and other components.
